	                    </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6" style="font-size: 14px;">
                        <h3 style="font-weight: bold;color:#326bb1;;"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;Collaborate</h3>
